00:02:45,725 --> 00:03:07,737
5 + 55 + 555 + ... + 555555555 equals 5 times 1 + 5 times 11 + 5 times 111 + ... + 5 times 111111111 equals 5 times (1 + 11 + 111 + ... + 111111111)

31
00:03:07,737 --> 00:03:10,475
Observe the sum inside the parentheses:

32
